<! [CDATA[
At Home Logo
At Home specializes in home decor and houseware products and is based in Plano, Texas and currently operates 225 stores in 40 states. The average store is 110,000 square feet. Each store offers up to 50,000 home products that range from furniture, mirrors, rugs, art and housewares to tabletop, patio and seasonal decor. In August 2016, the company went public. Lewis L. Bird III serves as Chairman of the Board and Chief Executive Officer for At Home.
You can download theAt Homelogo on full-version of the page.
